                  <summary>The Ms. contains only one text: I) Bārǝkanna ʾǝgziʾo… “Bless us, O
                     Lord…” (Blessing prayer)(fols. 3r-6r); II) Maṣḥafa gǝṣṣǝw, Lectionary for
                     the entire year (fols. 8ra-51rb); II-1) Scriptural readings for the days of
                     the week (fols. 8ra-32ra); II-2) Scriptural readings for liturgical
                     periods, fasts and feasts (for the entire year) (fols. 32ra-51rb);
                     Additio 1.</summary>

